text: Jamul may refer to: * Rancho Jamul, Mexican land grant in present-day San Diego County, California * Jamul Mountains, located in San Diego County, California * Jamul, California, an unincorporated community in San Diego County, California * Jamul, Durg, a nagar panchayat in Durg district in the Indian State of Chhattisgarh
title: Jamul
